latestIgtvVideos.title: EASY AND AESTHETIC STORY IDEAS FOR CLOUDSCAPES!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello everyone!
This is how you can make your stories look aesthetic and creative with just few simple steps! Monsoon is around the corner and everyone loves to capture how beautiful the sky looks. Keeping that in mind, I’ve added some easy and fun story editing ideas that will make your stories look ‘wow’.
I wanted to make a video about the basics and for beginners to practice in quarantine ( I’m a beginner too hihi) so I had limited options! Also, it’s about cloudscapes only sooo you know, you know! :((
Hope you guys like it. Share this video if you enjoyed!
Love love.
